{"tid":1813324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"電影界「手足」集氣! 力推中共禁片《返校》贏香港電影金像獎!","createTime":"2020-01-06T07:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T11:50:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":55,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"70094d2d2d15d6d95798a28285f337718ce0deb1","tid":1813324,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:51:25.000Z","msg":"《返校》 &mdash;&mdash; 一部在大陸被中共禁止討論的電影, 一部在香港遭多間戲院拒絕放映的電影.<br />\n<br />\n但幸好有各位手足支持, 而家《返校》香港票房破1000萬,&nbsp; 可以名正言順稱為「香港票房猛片」,&nbsp; 向親共建制陣營的打壓說不！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/72891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F72891&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=000917b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/72891</a><br />\n<br />\n而家《返校》剛入圍香港電影金像獎的「最佳亞洲華語電影」侯選片目. &nbsp;名單其他電影包括《流浪地球》, 《我和我的祖國》等大陸票房猛片.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfaa.com/doc/39th_asianmovielist.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfaa.com%2Fdoc%2F39th_asianmovielist.pdf&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=56ebc2f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfaa.com/doc/39th_asianmovielist.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n希望電影界「手足」集氣, 現在首先力推中共禁片《返校》獲得「最佳亞洲華語電影」提名, 再係之後既得獎投票力推《返校》奪獎.<br />\n 《返校》係中共VIP禁片, 如果可以係香港電影金像獎贏得「最佳亞洲華語電影」獎項,&nbsp; 絕對係為香港人文化史留下光榮紀錄, 電影界「手足」亦可向香港人證明 大部分電影界人士並非奶共!<br />\n<br />\n希望電影界「手足」集氣幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016f96dc16a1169f0f6b257c95b2f6c0ca1868a4","tid":1813324,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:51:36.000Z","msg":"有人可能話藝術大於一切<br />\n我既回應: 好電影都講求時間性<br />\n<br />\n2004年, 南韓經典《原罪犯》和反戰電影《華氏9/11》同時角遂康城影展大獎.<br />\n最後, 評判主席Quentin Tarantino選了反戰電影 《華氏9/11》奪得最高榮譽大獎.  <br />\nQuentin Tarantino解釋 :  因為《華氏9/11》非常切合2004年的時勢.   現在回看《華氏9/11》, 觀眾會覺得非常過時.  但對2004年的時勢而言, 《華氏9/11》絕對值得贏最佳電影.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/03/style/tmagazine/03taranw.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2009%2F05%2F03%2Fstyle%2Ftmagazine%2F03taranw.html&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=7f6eb889\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/03/style/tmagazine/03taranw.html</a><br />\n<em>&ldquo;Fahrenheit 9/11.&rdquo; You know what? As time has gone on, I&rsquo;ve put that decision under a microscope and I still think we were right. That was a movie of the moment &mdash; &ldquo;Fahrenheit 9/11&rdquo; may not play the same way now as it did then, but back then it deserved everything it got.</em><br />\n<br />\n在「最佳亞洲華語電影」侯選片目中, 我都非常鍾意《大象席地而坐》委.  但對2019年的時勢而言, 《返校》絕對值得贏「最佳亞洲華語電影」."},{"pid":"24e5493adc4e198c2d845db9a193c0f737578df6","tid":1813324,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"另外， 想舉辦「社區放映場」的朋友要留意<br />\n《返校》香港片方已在Facebook貼上以下電郵地址， 有傳是用作接受香港人申請舉辦「社區放映場」（但應要在電影落畫後才開始接受申請）<br />\nhkdetention@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 香港戲院繼續要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戲院場次<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkmovie6.com/movie/50623#showtimes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkmovie6.com%2Fmovie%2F50623%23showtimes&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=a71126a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkmovie6.com/movie/50623#showtimes</a><br />\n<br />\n預告片<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cq0K2ipTaPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCq0K2ipTaPM&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=5d7c1c4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cq0K2ipTaPM</a>"},{"pid":"9910956877e19947af5e29fd8e59c02a34128736","tid":1813324,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:58:55.000Z","msg":"推禁片<img src=\"/assets/fa